    "title": "Job Opening Category Manager at Shyaway Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Shyaway Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Shyaway Digital Technologies:\nShyaway Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shyaway Digital Technologies!",
